00:25:31,863 --> 00:25:34,783
Shit. Hey, go bring this! This thing!

383
00:25:36,201 --> 00:25:38,203
-Shit! What happened?
-Song Gi-hyeon!

384
00:25:39,079 --> 00:25:40,747
-Damn it.
-Hey!

385
00:25:41,248 --> 00:25:43,041
